the economy georgia is a major resort area and the fruit and 
vegetable basket of the soviet union there is also mining and 
industry 
</TEXT>
<TEXT>
political status georgia is one of the 15 republics making up 
the soviet union and activists are calling for secession abkhazia 
is an autonomous republic under the authority of georgia 
activists there want it to become a 16th republic of the soviet 
union 
</TEXT>
<TEXT>
history georgia is one of the oldest nations in the soviet 
union with records dating back to the 3rd century bc it became 
christian in ad 318 it became a part of the russian empire in 
1800 to gain protection from the persians it became part of the 
soviet union in 1921 
in 1956 dozens of people were killed when soviet troops fired 
on a memorial march for the late dictator josef stalin who was a 
georgian 
in april 1978 in tbilisi about 5000 people marched in protest 
of plans to drop georgian as the state language of the republic 
the plans were dropped 
</TEXT>
