copies of the complaint friday he said 
under house rules the formal filing of such a complaint by 
alexander will force the ethics committee to take a vote on whether 
to launch an investigation of gingrich a georgia republican 
alexanders action was seen as the beginning of a democratic 
counteroffensive against gingrich who last year filed the ethics 
complaint that resulted in a lengthy investigation of speaker jim 
wright dtexas 
