the nine allegations in alexanders complaint center on an 
unusual promotional deal for gingrichs 1984 book window of 
opportunity details of the deal were disclosed last month just 
before house republicans elected gingrich to their number two 
leadership position 
on friday gingrich said the complaint was clearly another 
democratic smear and in this case a pathetically poorly done 
